## ðŸš€ To Get Started:

**Follow the "Complete File Checklist & Quick Start" artifact above** - it has a step-by-step guide that takes just 5 minutes!

### Quick Commands:
```bash
# 1. Create structure
mkdir vulnerability-scanner && cd vulnerability-scanner
mkdir scanners utils playwright_scraper
touch scanners/__init__.py utils/__init__.py

# 2. Install Python deps
pip install Flask flask-cors requests

# 3. Install Node.js deps (in project root)
npm install playwright
npx playwright install chromium

# 4. Run backend
python app.py

# 5. Run frontend (in another terminal)
cd frontend && npm start
```

